                <p>Company Overview </p>
                <p class="main_text">
                      Apex International is a privately owned Miami based Transportation Company with offices in NY and LA. We have an established network of over 4000 affiliates throughout the US, Canada, and Worldwide. Our professionally trained executive staff has over 30 years of experience in the transportation industry. <br />
                </p>
                <p class="main_text">
                      At Apex we understand that it is our responsibility to make sure our clients travel in luxury and relaxing comfort. Apex offers an elegant, prompt and reliable transportation service 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, 365 days a year. We have a full line of corporate services, which include black corporate Lincoln Town Cars and Cadillac Sedans. Our luxury fleet consists of brand new Black Luxury L-series Lincoln Town-Car Sedans, Stretch Limousines, Black SUV’s, custom 14 passenger vans, and 24, 49, or 56-passenger coach buses.  <br />
                </p>
                <p class="main_text">
                      Our company’s unique infrastructure distinguishes us from our competitors. Operating our own 24-hour auto repair facility on premises, gives us an opportunity to provide our customers with elegant, safe, and uninterrupted service at all times. Our drivers are professionally trained and are highly experienced operators with an excellent knowledge of the Miami-Dade area. More than half of our fleet is equipped with a state of the art navigation system. In order to provide our customers with fast and dependable service the most advanced modern technology in the transportation industry has been installed in our facility. In addition, a professional team has been established in order to monitor all accounts with optimum efficiency and quality service. <br />
                </p>
                <p class="main_text">
                      The establishment of our affiliate network provides us with an extraordinary capability of making pick ups in any State, City, or district across the US, Canada, or anywhere around the World. Whether the pick up is in New York, Los Angeles, Miami, Anchorage Alaska, Boise Idaho, or Milan  Italy, one phone call to Apex can accommodate all your National or International pickup needs. A responsive caring staff member is always available to honor your requests.  <br />
                </p>
                <p class="main_text">
                      To assure satisfaction, Apex’ management team observes and fully monitors your trip, starting with a courtesy telephone call notifying you of a car number and an on-time pick up. With Apex, you will enjoy your course of travel and experience complete satisfaction at the end of your trip. We are big enough to serve big corporate accounts and small enough to provide a personal touch. <br />
                
                </p>
                <p  class="header1">
                      Apex helps you keep your eyes on your business, while we keep an eye on the road.
                </p>
                <p class="main_text">
                      Here at Apex we are eager to satisfy you, the client. That’s why we are constantly looking for new and improved ways to enhance our services. We take this responsibility very seriously and this attitude is emphasized with our drivers and staff. In recognition of the ever-changing demands of our clients our solutions are fully adaptable to easily accommodate an assortment of business cultures. Numerous state of the art back end technologies, which allow us to provide a one-stop shop for all your ground transportation needs, have already been implemented. Our drivers are completely aware of their important function and they will always try to maintain an acceptable level of polite service. All of us fully understand our role in the ground transportation industry and we pledge to undertake our obligations in a professional, polite, and cost efficient manner that lets us pass the savings on to our customers. <br />
                </p>
                <p class="main_text">
                      Apex values your business. We look forward to delivering quality service that will always exceed your expectations. <br />
                </p>
                <p class="header2" >
                      Apex Standards 
                </p>
                
